{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">InterCorruption is an indie turn-based RPG where you must defend Molly (the main character) against corrupted enemies. Battles combine familiar elements (timed button-press attacks and dodge, items, spells, etc.) with new mechanics (corruption/debugging).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>A playable demo will be available soon.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164210/extras/description_subtitle1.png?t=1730311921\" />You control Molly, an &quot;NPC&quot; living in a game that was abandoned back in the 90\u2019s and that is now slowly decaying. She speaks directly to you and will need your help to find a way to stop the corruption from spreading. Throughout the adventure, you will be navigating between two worlds: the \u201cnormal world\u201d and a scrapped build of the game known as the \u201cBeta world&quot;. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164210/extras/description_image.png?t=1730311921\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164210/extras/description_subtitle3.png?t=1730311921\" />During battles, you can make Molly jump, duck, or block attacks (depending on the attack itself). Most of Molly\u2019s attacks inflict more damage when timed correctly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164210/extras/description_animation2.gif?t=1730311921\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You must keep Molly\u2019s corruption meter low during battles, or the game will start to glitch and her stats will plummet. If the meter reaches 99%, it\u2019s game over! You can fix errors and reduce her corruption, but that costs \u201cmemory points\u201d.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Corruption is inflicted on Molly if she gets hit by corrupted enemies or if she attacks them directly. If an enemy's corruption is too high, you would be better off debugging them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164210/extras/description_image6.gif?t=1730311921\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Debugging enemies takes the form of retro-inspired mini-games. Once in \u201cdebug mode\u201d you must reduce the enemy\u2019s corruption as much as possible before the timer expires or Molly\u2019s corruption meter will start to increase rapidly!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164210/extras/description_debug_mode.png?t=1730311921\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164210/extras/description_subtitle4.png?t=1730311921\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A unique and dynamic battle system.</strong><br> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A highly interactive overworld where you can use items (bombs, tennis racket, etc.), lift objects, jump down ledges, and much more.</strong><br> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dungeons filled with puzzles, keys, switches, treasures, traps, and more.</strong><br> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A multi-layered story with a lot of twists, intrigues, and mysteries.</strong><br> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A main character that interacts with you and remembers your actions and choices.</strong><br> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Multiple outcomes and dialogue variations that depend on your choices.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>An original soundtrack mostly inspired by 16-bit era video games.</strong><br> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>An optional CRT filter.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164210/extras/crt_comparision.png?t=1730311921\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3164210?t=1730311921","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164210/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1730311921","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164210/2108f8ba9a5484895bd3c0789fa716a875150b1e/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1730311921","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164210/2108f8ba9a5484895bd3c0789fa716a875150b1e/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1730311921","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">InterCorruption is an indie turn-based RPG where you must defend Molly (the main character) against corrupted enemies. Battles combine familiar elements (timed button-press attacks and dodge, items, spells, etc.) with new mechanics (corruption/debugging).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>A playable demo will be available soon.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class